Space: O(1)

3. First Occurrence
Intuition

When target is found,

Don't stop.

Continue searching on the left side.

Java
class Solution {

    public int firstOccurrence(int[] nums, int target) {

        int low = 0;
        int high = nums.length - 1;
        int ans = -1;

        while (low <= high) {

            int mid = low + (high - low) / 2;

            if (nums[mid] == target) {
                ans = mid;
                high = mid - 1;
            }
            else if (nums[mid] < target) {
                low = mid + 1;
            }
            else {
                high = mid - 1;
            }
        }

        return ans;
    }
}
Example
nums = [1,2,2,2,3]
target = 2

Answer = 1

