Key Tricks
Classic Search: Stop immediately when the target is found.
First Occurrence: Store the answer and continue searching to the left.
Last Occurrence: Store the answer and continue searching to the right.
Lower Bound: Find the first index where nums[i] >= target.
Upper Bound: Find the first index where nums[i] > target.
